Return the usage of the pool as value between 0 and 1 (or -1 if the pool is not_limited)._
    _
  • 1 means that the maximum number of connections have been allocated
    • _
  • 0 means that no connection is currently active
    • _
  • -1 means there is not limit to the number of connections that can be allocated_
